    <bioghist id="bioghist">

	<p>	Please contact the College Archives for Ruth Bernstein's biographical information.</p>
    </bioghist>


    <scopecontent id="scope">

	<p>	This collection contains correspondence written by Ruth "Babs" Bernstein to her parents and sister "Mar". A dedicated correspondent, the collection includes daily and weekly correspondence from the entirety of her first year to her junior year at Smith College.  The collection also contains a few letters received during her time at Smith College as well as a number of pamphlets, flyers, and class notes from 1945 - 1949.</p>
    </scopecontent>    <arrangement encodinganalog="351$a" id="scope-org">

    	<p>This collection is organized into two series:</p>
    	<list>
    		<item>
    			Correspondence Sent (1945 - 1949)
    		</item>
    		<item>
    			Correspondence Received (1945 - 1949)
    		</item>
    	</list>
        </arrangement>


<!-- End collection level metadata -->


